                            <comment id="13840615" author="msahyoun" created="Thu, 5 Dec 2013 21:53:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Although it&#8217;s clear why this loop never ends could you attach the sample documents to verify their content?&lt;/p&gt;

